<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mò hòu de guāng jǐng 迦南674</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài yǐ qián yǐ qián de shí hòu, zhǔ gào sù wǒ mò hòu de guāng jǐng.
 nà shí rén yào zhuān gù zì jǐ, tān ài qián cái wú qīn qíng,
 ài yàn lè bù ài shén. yǒu jìng qián de wài biǎo, wú jìng qián de xīn líng.
 nǐ yào jǐng xǐng a, wǒ yào jǐng xǐng a. huí jiā méi yǒu jǐ chéng,
 měi yī tiān dōu yào xíng zài zhǔ de guāng míng zhōng. cái néng jiàn dài chōng mǎn, shēng mìng fēng shèng.
 zài zuì jiān nán de shí kè, yǔ zhǔ tóng xíng, jǐn zhōng zài jǐn zhōng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>674</hymn_number>
</song>